import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './NoVisitar.css'; function NoVisitar() { const [sidebarVisible, setSidebarVisible] = useState(true); const toggleSidebar = function(evento) { setSidebarVisible(!sidebarVisible); }; document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() { var searchInput = document.getElementById("searchInput"); var resultsList = document.getElementById("results"); var matchedElements = []; var currentIndex = 0; searchInput.addEventListener("input", function() { var searchTerm = searchInput.value.trim().toLowerCase(); resultsList.innerHTML = ""; if (searchTerm.length === 0) { return; } var elementsToSearch = document.querySelectorAll("body *"); matchedElements = []; elementsToSearch.forEach(function(element) { var text = element.textContent.toLowerCase(); if (text.includes(searchTerm)) { matchedElements.push(element); } }); }); document.getElementById("nextButton").addEventListener("click", function() { if (matchedElements.length === 0) { return; } currentIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % matchedElements.length; scrollToElement(matchedElements[currentIndex]); }); document.getElementById("prevButton").addEventListener("click", function() { if (matchedElements.length === 0) { return; } currentIndex = (currentIndex - 1 + matchedElements.length) % matchedElements.length; scrollToElement(matchedElements[currentIndex]); }); function scrollToElement(element) { element.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth", block: "center" }); } }); function showNotification({top = 0, right = 0, className, html}) { let notification = document.createElement('div'); notification.className = "notification"; if (className) { notification.classList.add(className); } notification.style.top = top + 'px'; notification.style.right = right + 'px'; notification.innerHTML = html; document.body.append(notification); } showNotification({ top: 10, right: 10, html: "Nuevo anuncio", className: "welcome" }); return (
